data.description: Welcome to this charming  home nestled in the picturesque town of Provincetown, MA. This property is perched atop a hill, offering  views of the serene Clapps Pond and is enveloped by scenic conservation land. Can be single family homeThe residence boasts numerous updates, including a newer roof, furnace, and windows, ensuring both comfort and peace of mind for the fortunate new owners. Each unit has its own distinct charm - one featuring a cozy one-bedroom layout, and the other offering a more spacious two-bedroom configuration.Step outside onto your private deck and soak in the natural beauty that surrounds you. With plenty of parking available and a convenient shed for storage, this property provides both functionality and convenience.Inside, both units feature modern amenities, including newer appliances and the added convenience of a washer/dryer in each unit. Whether you're a savvy investor seeking an income-generating property or a buyer looking for a move-in ready home, this opportunity ticks all the boxes.  Situated on a tranquil cul-de-sac, the location adds an extra layer of privacy to this already idyllic setting. Use as two family or single family
